JsAuthorization
===============

Simple authorization plugin.

It handle login, signup, forgot_password and of course new_password.

Installation
=======

Of course first get the plugin.

1. ruby script/plugin install git://github.com/jamalsoueidan/js_authorization.git

Then we use the js_formbuilder to create the login, signup etc. forms. So get that too.

2. ruby script/plugin install git://github.com/jamalsoueidan/js_formbuilder.git

and last generate the files over the your project.

3. ruby script/generate js_authorization


Finished ;)



